data.description: Immerse yourself in the breathtaking beauty surrounding this move-in-ready Big Bear cabin, peacefully set amid towering trees on a gently sloping lot! From the picturesque covered porch, enter an open-concept interior with vibrant tones and gorgeous hardwood-style flooring. Brilliant sunlight fills the heights of the exposed vaulted ceilings soaring over the seamlessly connected gathering areas. Imagine coming home after a long day to sip a refreshing nightcap in the warmth of the living room’s striking brick fireplace. Use your creative skills to transform the fully equipped kitchen into the modern culinary space of your dreams. What could be better than waking up to the sounds of nature within the well-proportioned bedroom, accommodated by a full bath? When you want to enjoy the fresh air and magnificent views, head to the shaded patio and generous, fenced-in backyard featuring a detached shed and workshop. With hiking, skiing, shopping, and dining just a short drive away, why wait? Come for a tour while it’s still available!
